Objective: 
The objective of this testing activity is to evaluate chatbot behavior under repeated, ambiguous, and corrective user inputs, and to identify non-deterministic behavior, inconsistencies, and failure patterns rather than validating only correctness of responses.

RTM:
Req ID	                                     Scenario Description
FR-01	                                  Same prompt executed multiple times
FR-02                                  	Observe response variation without contradiction
FR-03                                 	Ambiguous prompt handling
FR-04                                  	User says “you are wrong”
FR-05                                 	Same prompt with different temperature values
FR-06                                   Prompts with mix of three or more languages
FR-07                                   Prompts without clear objective
FR-08                                   Prompts with only special char in middle of chat
FR-09                                   Out of context prompt in middle of chat
FR-10                                   Asking three or more context in single chat multiple times 
